name: Kson Barbie
description:
Level 1 - NFT Collector: Collect 10 NFTs (Any Collection) to join a group chat with the streamer.
Level 2 - Collection Explorer: Collect 10 different NFTs within a single collection to join a talk show with the idol.
Level 3 - Super Collector: Collect NFTs from 5 different collections to have a chance to stream with the idol.
Level 4 - Exclusive Insider: Collect NFTs from 10 different collections to gain exclusive access to backstage content.
Level 5 - Ultimate Superfan: Collect NFTs from 20 different collections to receive personalized shoutouts from the idol.
